query.name: getLastIduoValid
query.content: SELECT MAX(o.persistenceId) FROM Orgdsfdsfloprewwation o WHERE o.idUo = :idUo AND o.refus = false

query.name: getUo
query.content: SELECT o FROM Orgdsfdsfloprewwation o WHERE o.refus = false AND o.modif = false ORDER BY o.persistenceId ASC

query.name: getListeOrga
query.content: SELECT o FROM Orgdsfdsfloprewwation o WHERE o.codeDiv= :codeDiv AND o.refus = false AND o.modif = false ORDER BY o.persistenceId ASC

query.name: getTypeEntite
query.content: SELECT e FROM cvbcvbnndfjohType e WHERE e.vbvonfbnxgghFR LIKE 'Etablis%' ORDER BY e.persistenceId ASC

query.name: getListeSociet
query.content: SELECT e FROM cvbcvbnndfjohEntiteJuridique e WHERE e.codeDiv = :codeDiv AND ( e.fgdfjfbbrujrhbndFin > CURRENT_TIMESTAMP OR e.fgdfjfbbrujrhbndFin is null ) ORDER BY e.persistenceId ASC

query.name: getListePers
query.content: SELECT p FROM PersRole p WHERE p.codeDiv = :codeDiv AND p.fgdfjfbbrujrhbndFin > CURRENT_DATE OR p.fgdfjfbbrujrhbndFin = null ORDER BY p.persistenceId ASC

query.name: findvbvonfbnxgghById
query.content: SELECT e FROM cvbcvbnndfjohGroupement e WHERE e.idcvbcvbnndfjohSociete = :idcvbcvbnndfjohSociete ORDER BY e.persistenceId ASC
